data.description: Been looking for a well-maintained brick home on a beautiful in-town 1/2 acre lot with a private backyard?! This is it! And so much to offer! Comfy, efficient radiant heated floors, large 3-seasons porch heated by a toasty newer gas fireplace, electric built-in living room fireplace (can be converted back to wood-burning), HUGE 2-level deck where you can entertain or take in the scenic backyard view, LOTS of off-street parking on newer (2010) concrete driveway, beautiful stamped-concrete entry walkway, new sewer pipe (no orangeburg!) 2010, newer iron fencing, new roof 2020, new carpet in dining & living rooms 2021. Large formal dining room & informal dining too! A surplus of kitchen countertops & cabinets & a 1st floor laundry!  PLUS a one-car storage garage in the back yard! Sold As-Is, inspections for buyer info only. Add your finishing touches to make it your own and enjoy easy access to shopping, schools and more!
